</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>For the name Unio, see Robert, Gladiateurs, 232 and 301, with OMS IV, 175. For Pardalas as the name of a mime see <xref type="iAph">601</xref>.ii, and of a gladiator, Gladiateurs no. 269, and 300</p>
</div>
